address2: Units B1901 on level 19 & B2001 on level 20 No. 26 Chaowai Street Chaoyang District
longBusinessSummary: Futong Technology Development Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides enterprise digital transformation services in the People's Republic of China and Hong Kong. The company offers enterprise information technology infrastructure products, services, and solutions; cloud computing management products; and intelligent digitalized application products. It also offers value-added system integration services comprising presale technical program advice, after-sale product installation, tuning, optimization, and operation and maintenance services. The company was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.
